radiographic_examinations.findings: Hyperintensity in the right thalamocapsular region and right midbrain, with patchy enhancement of the right midbrain.
Resolution of the hyperintensity that had been seen previously. Hyperintensity of the optic-nerve heads and prominence of the CSF space surrounding the optic nerves.
Dominant right transverse sinus, with narrowing of the distal transverse sinuses bilaterally.
